# 🎯 SkillQuest – Career Discovery

A beginner-friendly Python mini project that helps users discover a suitable technology career based on their interests, favorite subject, strengths, and skill level.

Developed as part of the **AI Powered Python Internship** using **Python Fundamentals**, **HTML**, and **CSS** on **Google Colab**.

---

## 📌 Project Overview

SkillQuest is an interactive career guidance application that asks users a few simple questions and recommends a suitable IT career path.

The project demonstrates Python fundamentals while generating an attractive HTML-based career report.

---

