## 🚀 How to Run

### Google Colab

1. Open Google Colab.
2. Upload the Python file.
3. Run all cells.
4. Enter your details.
5. View your personalized career report.

### Local Machine

```bash
python SkillQuest_Career_Discovery.py
```

> **Note:** The HTML report is best viewed in Google Colab because it uses `IPython.display.HTML`.

